I'll get you out of here.

12
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,120
I won't let him get his hands on us.

13
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,980
I won't let him get his hands on us.

14
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,800
One lives.

15
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:24,070
Two die.

16
