24
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:14,550
People are trying to sleep here!

25
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,360
Are you crazy?

26
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,630
1.8 million followers,

27
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:34,920
6 million likes.

28
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,360
More than that, it's still growing.

29
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:39,720
These fans

30
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:41,120
cast their gazes on me,

31
00:06:41,430 --> 00:06:42,830
give me their attention,

32
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,070
and think of me day and night.

33
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:46,600
They

34
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,600
are my believers.

35
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,890
Worship generates spiritual power.

36
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,159
I'll become more and more powerful

37
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:58,760
and more and more beautiful.

38
