As an influencer,

43
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,000
you're absorbing the power of worship

44
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,160
and admiration

45
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,680
every minute and every second,

46
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,270
with no restriction of region

47
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,310
or time.

48
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,070
You could even say...

49
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,240
I'm like a god.

50
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,040
You should feel honored,

51
00:07:27,950 --> 00:07:28,800
because you

52
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:29,930
are witnessing

53
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:31,830
the birth of a new god.

54
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:33,830
Yan Yuzhen—

55
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,270
the Venus

56
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:41,360
of the new world.

57
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,310
Dongqing!

58
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:48,270
Yan Yuzhen?

59
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,070
Zhao Li?

60
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,720
You ruined my painting.

61
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,320
I hate you.

62
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:53,430
I won't take the blame for this.

63
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:54,290
I'm not Zhao Li.

64
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:55,310
I'm Zhao Hengzhi.

65
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,190
I'm not a ferryman,

66
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:56,950
but a night watchman.

67
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,550
I just changed my hairstyle.

68
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:00,750
So you're human.

69
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:03,230
What's a night watchman?

70
00:08:03,430 --> 00:08:04,950
A night watchman is...

71
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:06,630
That Yan Yuzhen—

72
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:07,870
why does she look like a foreigner?

73
00:08:07,870 --> 00:08:09,680
That nose looks like it's been done.

74
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,750
You're even more annoying than Zhao Li.

75
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:12,280
He's more annoying than me.

76
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,620
Smell this. What is it?

77
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:18,010
It smells a bit off.

78
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:21,070
I've never smelled
anything like this before.

79
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:23,530
It was left behind by
that demonic creature.

80
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,200
It's amniotic fluid.

81
00:08:32,030 --> 00:08:33,030
How do you know?

82
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:35,000
Before marrying Sanlang,

83
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,549
I had a child with the Prince of Shou.

84
00:08:36,549 --> 00:08:37,549
It was a daughter.

85
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:39,030
She didn't get to grow up.

86
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,789
Such things

87
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:44,960
would not be

88
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,240
recorded in history.

89
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:51,270
I think it was a Guhuo Bird.

90
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,510
Guhuo Bird?

91
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:55,390
The demon
that specifically kidnaps children?

92
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:57,050
Women who lose their children

93
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,120
or die in childbirth

94
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:01,080
are said to turn into a demon

95
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:03,510
called the Guhuo Bird
because of their overwhelming resentment.

96
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,080
Wherever a Guhuo Bird appears,

97
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,840
it leaves behind a substance

98
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,360
similar to amniotic fluid.

99
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,030
Did that person have a child with them?

100
00:09:09,030 --> 00:09:10,030
Not necessarily.

101
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,270
The Guhuo Bird

102
00:09:11,390 --> 00:09:12,270
is a monster often associated

103
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,390
with babies.

104
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,320
I guess...

105
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:18,440
No need to guess.

106
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,200
It's here.

107
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:58,490
[Account Balance]
[Available Balance: 3.68 yuan]

108
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:06,840
Baby.

109
00:10:08,260 --> 00:10:09,500
I'm sorry.

110
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:13,160
I don't have any money left.

111
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:18,270
But don't worry.

112
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:22,040
I'll definitely find a way—

113
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,700
a way to bring you into this world.

114
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:36,390
Hello.

115
00:10:37,790 --> 00:10:39,520
You came by our café yesterday.

116
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:41,840
Convenience Store 444.

117
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:48,510
It's so late.

118
00:10:49,030 --> 00:10:50,490
Why aren't you going home?

119
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,240
I can't go home.

120
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:53,320
Why?

121
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,650
There's a demon chasing me.

122
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:02,750
A demon?

123
00:11:03,150 --> 00:11:04,080
It's my husband.

124
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:07,220
He died and turned into a demon.

125
00:11:07,220 --> 00:11:08,000
He wants to take me

126
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,940
and my unborn baby

127
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:10,140
down to hell with him.

128
00:11:23,310 --> 00:11:24,100
Thank you.

129
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:32,670
Eat more.

130
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,790
With all this drifting
from place to place,

131
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:35,760
your baby

132
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:37,000
probably can't take it.

133
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,330
He might follow me here.

134
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,840
I ran away from home.

135
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,600
But no matter where I run,

136
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,600
he tracks me down.

137
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,720
Do you have any mirrors in this café?

138
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,320
Mirrors?

139
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:50,630
What about mirrors?

140
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:52,240
Anything that reflects light

141
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,960
can serve as a medium for demons,

142
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,160
especially mirrors.

143
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,600
Every time,

144
00:11:57,050 --> 00:11:58,200
it's through the mirror

145
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,400
that I see my husband.

146
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:02,000
When did

147
00:12:02,020 --> 00:12:03,350
your husband pass away?

148
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:04,550
Last year.

149
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:09,040
Around this time last year.

150
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:10,480
Last year?

151
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,540
Is the baby you're carrying

152
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:18,120
his?

153
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:21,000
What's that supposed to mean?

154
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,060
Of course it's his!

155
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,090
When your husband passed away,

156
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,600
how many months pregnant were you?

157
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,400
Seven months.

158
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,270
It's been a year.

159
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,360
You've been pregnant with this child

160
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,510
for 19 months.

161
00:12:38,390 --> 00:12:39,700
Nineteen months?

162
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:42,870
Why is that?

163
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:44,440
I...

164
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:45,670
I...

165
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:47,840
I can't remember.

166
00:12:48,650 --> 00:12:50,050
How did your husband die?

167
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,360
I...

168
00:12:54,730 --> 00:12:55,530
Hang in there!

169
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:01,750
Careful.

170
00:13:07,710 --> 00:13:08,590
I was bleeding,

171
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,930
and he was very anxious.

172
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:11,870
Worried about getting stuck in traffic,

173
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:14,130
he carried me all the way to the hospital.

174
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,840
One dies,

175
00:13:18,390 --> 00:13:19,630
two live.

176
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:23,910
One dies, two live...

177
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:27,320
One dies, two live!

178
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:28,840
Dongqing.

179
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,060
That's enough.

180
00:13:35,270 --> 00:13:36,270
Don't be nervous.

181
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:37,960
We were just asking.

182
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:38,750
You...

183
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:40,350
What do you guys want?

184
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,030
Why do you keep

185
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:43,390
asking about my husband?

186
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:44,480
Who exactly are you?

187
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,610
Don't get worked up.

188
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:47,600
Don't you want to

189
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:50,120
see for yourself?

190
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,070
Hello, what do you...

191
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,330
Do you have any food?

192
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:45,840
ID card.

193
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,130
Do you remember now?

194
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,540
You're afraid of mirrors.

195
00:15:04,590 --> 00:15:05,990
What you saw in the mirror

196
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:08,000
was yourself.

197
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,200
One dies, two live—

198
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:13,510
that's what you've always thought.

199
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:15,760
Who was the one that died?

200
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:27,510
[In Surgery]

201
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:25,840
Doctor.

202
00:15:26,660 --> 00:15:27,390
How did it go?

203
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:28,030
I'm sorry,

204
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:29,910
but we failed to save the baby.

205
00:15:29,910 --> 00:15:30,370
Then...

206
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:31,960
Then...

207
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:33,760
Then what about my wife?

208
00:15:34,150 --> 00:15:36,630
I'm sorry. She lost too much blood.

209
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:38,560
No way...

210
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:41,280
Her blood type is very rare,

211
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,150
and we couldn't find

212
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:43,610
enough for a transfusion.

213
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,120
No way...

214
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,600
No way!

215
00:15:54,630 --> 00:15:55,790
I'm not me.

216
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:00,200
I'm not me.

217
00:16:01,390 --> 00:16:02,360
I'm not me.

218
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,000
I'm not me!

219
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:07,480
I'm not me! I'm not me!

220
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:08,960
I'm not me.

221
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,000
I'm not me.

222
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:14,630
I'm not me.

223
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:17,790
I'm not me.

224
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:18,670
One dies,

225
00:16:20,870 --> 00:16:21,720
two live.

226
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:24,200
You thought if one died,

227
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,750
the other two could live.

228
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:29,980
You chose to give up your own life.

229
00:16:30,330 --> 00:16:31,120
You erased your own identity

230
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,030
from your mind

231
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:34,720
and became your wife and child.

232
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:36,840
My wife...

233
00:16:38,550 --> 00:16:39,440
And my child...

234
00:16:42,150 --> 00:16:44,010
They've always been by your side,

235
00:16:44,740 --> 00:16:45,810
trying their best

236
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:46,790
to wake you up,

237
00:16:47,630 --> 00:16:48,790
even at the cost

238
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:52,910
of turning themselves into demons.

239
00:16:58,720 --> 00:16:59,550
Meihui...

240
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,840
Meihui!

241
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:33,920
Meihui.

242
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,160
Meihui...

243
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:03,040
Although it's hard to let go,

244
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:05,400
you still

245
00:18:07,510 --> 00:18:09,170
have to move on with your life.

246
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:15,310
Meihui...

247
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:20,960
The love that's gone

248
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:24,490
doesn't want you to stay trapped
in delusion.

249
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:27,160
It has become a guiding light of wisdom,

250
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:29,840
hoping only that you wake up

251
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:34,160
and live your life well.

252
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:43,720
Thank you for helping me fulfill my wish.

253
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:53,650
Now I'm sure

254
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:54,740
you're not Zhao Li.

255
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:55,680
Why?

256
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:59,060
That brat Zhao never sheds tears.

257
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:01,880
Get lost already.

